<section class="page-header">
  <div class="page-header-inner">
    <div class="page-eyebrow">
      <a href="../index.html">Resource Center</a>
    </div>
    <h1>Know Your Rights</h1>
    <p class="lede">As an Iranian American, understanding your legal rights is one of the most important things you can do to protect yourself and your family. Whether you are a U.S. citizen, a permanent resident, or here on a visa, certain fundamental protections apply to you under the Constitution and federal law.</p>
    <p class="updated">Updated as of April 30, 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

<nav class="subnav" aria-label="Know Your Rights sub-pages">
  <div class="subnav-inner">
    <a href="index.html" class="is-current">Overview</a>
    <a href="police-ice.html">Police &amp; ICE Encounters</a>
    <a href="at-home.html">Rights at Home</a>
