<section class="article">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prose" style="max-width: 80ch;">
      <p>This section walks you through your rights in practical, everyday terms. Pick the situation closest to what you are facing — or read in order. Every page ends with primary-source citations you can verify.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 0;">

      <a class="card" href="police-ice.html">
        <h3 class="card-title">Police &amp; ICE Encounters</h3>
        <p class="card-desc">What to say, what you must provide, and the difference between being stopped, detained, and arrested. Plus the difference between a judicial warrant and an ICE administrative warrant.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Open guide</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="at-home.html">
        <h3 class="card-title">Rights at Home</h3>
        <p class="card-desc">Your home receives the strongest Fourth Amendment protection. The questions to ask before opening the door and the words that preserve your rights.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Open guide</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="airports-borders.html">
        <h3 class="card-title">Airports &amp; Borders</h3>
        <p class="card-desc">Rights at CBP secondary inspection, consular notification risks for dual nationals, Iranian military service obligations, and the State Department Iran travel advisory.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Open guide</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="discrimination.html">
        <h3 class="card-title">Discrimination</h3>
        <p class="card-desc">Federal anti-discrimination protections at work, in housing, in public places, and at school — and how to file a complaint when something happens.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Open guide</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="sanctions.html">
        <h3 class="card-title">U.S. Sanctions on Iran</h3>
        <p class="card-desc">Sending money home, what FBAR is, why a bank can’t close your account just for being Iranian, and what U.S. sanctions actually restrict — explained in plain language.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Open guide</span>
      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="callout callout-info" style="margin-top: 56px; max-width: 80ch;">
      <div class="callout-title">A printable rights card is available</div>
      <p>A wallet-sized card with these key phrases in English and Farsi — designed to keep near your front door or in your wallet — is in the <a href="../templates.html">Templates &amp; Cards</a> collection.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

